# COMPONENT SYSTEM RULES (FacePe)

## Global

- Every marketing **section** is a self-contained partial: `components/{section-id}.html` (or equivalent) with one root `section` node.
- **Cards** share: `rounded-card` + `shadow-card` + `p-6 md:p-8` (Figma `24px` inner padding on product cards).
- **No orphan styles:** if two sections use the same card chrome, they share one utility bundle.

## Site header

- **Height:** `h-[100px]` desktop; inner row `h-14` vertically centered.
- **Sticky:** `sticky top-0 z-50 bg-surface-0 border-b border-border-subtle` (adjust token names to match `tailwind.config.js`).
- **CTA position:** right cluster `Contact us` (text) + `Get Started` (gradient pill).
- **Mobile:** hamburger + drawer; preserve **primary CTA** in header bar when possible.

## Site footer

- **Grid:** `grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5` with column 1 = brand + socials (`44px` tap targets).
- **Link columns:** Product, Solutions, Company, Resources (labels from Home footer metadata).
- **Legal row:** full-width divider, `flex-col md:flex-row md:justify-between gap-4`.

## Section structure (order)

1. Optional **eyebrow** (`12px`, uppercase, `brand-600`, wide tracking).
2. **H2** (or H1 in hero only).
3. **Supporting** copy (`18px`, `leading-[28px]`).
4. **CTA row** (max 2 pills + optional text links).
5. **Media / grid**.

## Feature & product cards

- **Radius:** `28px` token.
- **Padding:** `24px` inner (`p-6`).
- **Top row:** `44px` icon tile + category pill (`h-6`, `px-3`, uppercase `text-[15px]`).
- **Hover:** `translate-y-[-2px]` + shadow token bump (see `animation-rules.mdc`).
- **Footer link:** “Learn more” + chevron `14px` — use Lucide `ArrowRight` or `ChevronRight` at `w-3.5 h-3.5`.

## Stats card

- **Number:** `~44px` bold.
- **Label:** `~21px` medium/bold per token.
- **Supporting line:** `~20px` regular.
- **Dividers:** `border-t border-border-subtle` between stat rows.

## Testimonial

- Quote → body → **avatar row** (`48px` square, gradient allowed) → name (`22px`) + title (`16px` muted).
- Pagination dashes under testimonial: decorative `aria-hidden="true"`.

## FAQ

- **Two-column `lg+`:** intro left (`max-w-md`), questions right (`max-w-[640px]`).
- **Row height (closed):** `~81px`; **open first item** shows answer block (`~72px`+ text).
- **Trigger:** `button` `32×32` visual with **44px** hit slop; `aria-expanded` + `aria-controls`.

## Buttons

- **Primary:** gradient + `shadow-primary` + `h-14` + `px-5` + `gap-2.5` + `rounded-pill`.
- **Secondary:** `bg-surface-0 border border-border-subtle text-ink-950 h-14 px-5 rounded-[42px]` (tokenize as `rounded-pill-secondary`).
- **Icon:** `16px` left of label on CTAs.

## Pills / badges

- **Category pills:** subtle fill on white, uppercase, **`15px`** tracking normal, **bold**.
- **Do not** use pills for eyebrows—eyebrows are plain uppercase text.

## DO NOT

- Create a second “outline purple” button style—only **white + gray border** secondary exists in Figma.
- Duplicate the FAQ row markup with different class orders—extract partial.
